Package com.eventApp.DataStructures

Class MyEventLL

java.lang.Object
com.eventApp.DataStructures.MyEventLL
public class MyEventLL extends Object
Custom doubly linked list implementation for managing Event objects. Supports insertion sorted by event date, navigation, and deletion at the current pointer. Maintains size and current node references for traversal and manipulation.

    • deleteAtCurrent

      public Event deleteAtCurrent()
      Deletes the Event at the current pointer. Adjusts pointers to maintain list integrity. Advances current pointer to the next node or resets to first if needed.
      Returns:
      the deleted Event, or null if list is empty

    • viewCurrentEvent

    • viewNextEvent

      public Event viewNextEvent()
      Moves the current pointer to the next Event and returns it. Returns null if at the end of the list or if current is null.

      the next Event, or null if none exists

    • viewPreviousEvent
